[I] WxWidgets GUI for Maxima

[T] wxMaxima is a wxWidgets GUI for the computer algebra system maxima.
[T]
[T] Since it is written with wxWidgets, it runs on multiple platforms in
[T] native widget sets. Most of maxima functions are accessible through
[T] menus, some have dialogs. The input line has command history (up-key,
[T] down-key) and completion based on previous input (tab-key). wxMaxima
[T] provides 2d formated display of maxima output.

[U] https://wxmaxima-developers.github.io/wxmaxima/

